Usage: deleteBumps [-help] [-all] [-bumps <bump+>] [-floating]
                   [-overlap_areaio] [-overlap_blockages]
                   [-overlap_keepout <bumpCellName>] [-overlap_macro]
                   [-selected]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-all                                # deletes all bumps (bool, optional)
-bumps <bump+>                      # specifies the bumps to be deleted
                                    # ((bump)+, optional)
-floating                           # Deletes bumps which are not assigned to
                                    # any nets (bool, optional)
-overlap_areaio                     # deletes all bumps that overlap the area
                                    # I/O cells (bool, optional)
-overlap_blockages                  # deletes all bumps that overlap routing
                                    # blockages (bool, optional)
-overlap_keepout <bumpCellName>     # Deletes specified bumps overlapping bump
                                    # keep out zone (string, optional)
-overlap_macro                      # deletes all bumps that overlap the
                                    # selected macros (bool, optional)
-selected                           # deletes selected bumps (bool, optional)